categories: Category:Jedi trainees of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: Galdos Stouff was a Jedi padawan who served the Jedi Order prior to and during the Clone Wars. Stouff, alongside their master Sora Bulq, fought in the First Battle of Geonosis as a member of the Jedi assault team, where they defeated a dozen encircling Geonosian guards.
